    Sexual Assault        3.5          21.1         21.1         45.7    

    Robbery              17.7          18.1         17.3         53.1    

    Assault               4.5          44.3          9.8         58.7    

    Other violent        10.0          21.8         27.3         59.2    

Property Offenses        18.2          17.9         12.8         48.9    

Drug Offenses            28.6          7.3          12.3         48.2    

