http://206.61.184.43:80/schaffer/ACTIVIST/dangers.htm 206.61.184.43 19970122115442 text/html 10582
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 11:54:33 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1f (S/N wpo-0deb)
